These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, july, august
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, billiard, chess
1. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing chess is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Birthday   | july | june  | december   | august    |
| Game     | monopoly     | billiard    | chess    | scrabble      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, animation, spy, thriller
City: nizza, venice, london, berlin
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
7. the person watching drama movies is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | drama | thriller  | animation |
| City     | berlin        | london  | venice    | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, frog, snake
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, woodworking, skydiving, video-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the snake##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the frog##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | goldfish | turtle   | snake     | frog     |
| Hobby   | woodworking  | video-games | skydiving   | traveling  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, dutch, polish, turkish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, coffee, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
2. the dutch is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the polish##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the polish is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | colombian  | turkish   | polish     | dutch |
| Beverage   | coffee  | hot-chocolate      | sprite        | iced-tea     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi, avocado, cucumber
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person eating cucumber is the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person eating avocado is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
7. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1
8. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Food   | cranberry   | cucumber   | avocado | kiwi |
| Beverage         | water      | soy-milk | tea      | iced-tea |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

