.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, kiwi, lemon, pepper
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, surfing, volleyball
4 different games are played: chess, poker, mah-jongg, domino
1. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person playing chess is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lemon   | pepper      | kiwi       | apricot |
| Sport   | cricket | volleyball | surfing     | ice-hockey |
| Game     | domino     | poker  | chess | mah-jongg |

