.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: grapes, peach, lemon, orange
City: venice, edinburgh, berlin, paris
1. the person traveling to berlin is the person eating grapes##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person eating orange and the person traveling to venice##2
3. the person eating orange is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person eating grapes is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Food   | lemon     | peach | orange   | grapes     |
| City           | venice | edinburgh         | paris         | berlin |

