.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, french, british, polish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower, daisy, rose
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the person who growsdaisy is the dutch##1
3. the person who growsrose is the british##1
4. the british is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the person who growsbellflower and the dutch##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
7. the dutch is in an even position##4
8. the dutch is between the french and the british##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality         | french | dutch      | british       | polish    |
| Flower           | sunflower  | daisy  | rose | bellflower |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

