.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, prince, fonseca
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, august, november, january
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
2. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
9. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Cigar   | oliveros         | havana  | prince     | fonseca         |
| Birthday        | january | august | april | november         |
| Sport      | rugby         | skiing  | ice-hockey   | weightlifting |

