.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pepper, cabbage, mango
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, manager, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, november, august
1. the person eating avocado is on the far left or far right##3
2. the librarian is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the manager##3
4. the librarian is in an even position##4
5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the librarian##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the librarian##1
8. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
9. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Food      | avocado                | mango  | pepper | cabbage   |
| Job           | software-developer | librarian | fisherman   | manager |
| Birthday   | october         | january     | august     | november |

