.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, lime, peach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, soccer, badminton, water-polo
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, musician, entrepreneur, videographer
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the musician is on the left or right of the videographer##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the scientist is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the videographer##2
6. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Sport   | water-polo | soccer | biathlon | badminton |
| Job   | entrepreneur    | scientist     | videographer    | musician |

