.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, disaster, action
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, golf, lacrosse, cycling
1. the person who's sport is golf is between the person watching disaster movies and the argentine##2
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person watching adventure movies##1
9. the turkish is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is handball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | adventure | disaster      | thriller  | action    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Sport           | cycling      | lacrosse       | golf   | handball      |

