.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, october, may
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, crime, animation, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person watching satire movies##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | december    | october | july  | may  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | crime       | fantasy | satire |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

