.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, social-worker, doctor, videographer
House: cape-cod, art-deco, craftsman, colonial
1. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
2. the art-deco house is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the social-worker##1
4. the person drinking cola is the videographer##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the writer is the art-deco house##1
7. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the colonial house is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Job   | videographer | writer      | social-worker | doctor |
| House           | craftsman   | art-deco  | cape-cod     | colonial |

