.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, tea
There 4 different types of food: corn, lettuce, pepper, apricot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, time-travel, family, mystery
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person eating pepper##2
6. the person watching zombie movies is the person eating apricot##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person eating corn is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Food       | pepper   | corn | lettuce | apricot |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | family      | time-travel    | zombie   |

