.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different games are played: canasta, poker, mah-jongg, whist
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lavender, amber, azure
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is between the german and the person playing whist##2
3. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
4. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person playing whist is the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Game          | poker | whist  | canasta   | mah-jongg    |
| Color   | red  | amber     | azure | lavender |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | russian | colombian | german   |

