.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian, brazilian, mexican
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, prince, bongani, montecristo
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the spanish##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the mexican and the spanish##2
6. the nigerian is on the left of the spanish##1
7. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian | spanish | brazilian      |
| Cigar     | prince   | bluemaster        | montecristo   | bongani       |

 